      </div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Affordable Pricing</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Quality education at prices that won't break the bank. Pay once, learn for a year.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
